            </h1>
            <p class="mb-2 opacity-70" style="color: hsl(32, 38%, 16%)">
                Creating an account allows you to view auction results,
                discover more, stay up to date and manage your activity.
            </p>
            <div style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); opacity: 0.7; border-radius: 15px; padding: 0.5em;">
              <h6>
                  .. Use this credentials to explore my website ..<br />
                  Happy journey <i class="bi bi-emoji-smile"></i>
              </h6>
              <p>
                  Email:
                  <span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Click to save link to cilpboard" onclick="copy(this)" style="cursor: pointer;" class="text-dark font-weight-bold" id="copyLink">saladin@yahoo.com</span>
